  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" > </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>Santa’s Shadow</i> is an indie horror experience that pits the player against a crazed family member. The goal is to escape by any means nescessary.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><i>Santa’s Shadow:</i> a tale of grief, obsession, and madness.</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >After the tragic death of his son on Christmas three years ago, a once-devoted husband begins to spiral. As Christmas grew closer, his behavior grew more erratic. His wife, desperate to understand, confronted him-and the nightmare began.<br><br>It is Christmas eve and you were invited for dinner. When you arrive, things take a turn for the worse. As you explore the home, you’ll uncover cryptic notes, solve environmental puzzles, and piece together what happened. </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Key Features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Resource Management: Make use of any and every source of light you can before it runs out.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Puzzles: Search the house in order to find a way out.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Atomospheric fog and Christmas/seasonal decorations. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Hiding: Get away from the enemy by utilizing your surroundings. </p></li></ul>",
  "about_the_game": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" > </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>Santa’s Shadow</i> is an indie horror experience that pits the player against a crazed family member. The goal is to escape by any means nescessary.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><i>Santa’s Shadow:</i> a tale of grief, obsession, and madness.</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >After the tragic death of his son on Christmas three years ago, a once-devoted husband begins to spiral. As Christmas grew closer, his behavior grew more erratic. His wife, desperate to understand, confronted him-and the nightmare began.<br><br>It is Christmas eve and you were invited for dinner. When you arrive, things take a turn for the worse. As you explore the home, you’ll uncover cryptic notes, solve environmental puzzles, and piece together what happened. </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Key Features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Resource Management: Make use of any and every source of light you can before it runs out.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Puzzles: Search the house in order to find a way out.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Atomospheric fog and Christmas/seasonal decorations. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Hiding: Get away from the enemy by utilizing your surroundings. </p></li></ul>",
